{"tid":1095585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胃痛死愛國社工經常關注跨境學童，亦經常參與內地交流活動","createTime":"2019-04-07T06:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T08:51:32.000Z","uid":42188,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9dff17db596ca593374815cb33b5ec86bacc9ea","tid":1095585,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"柴灣一名36歲姓陳男子，昨晚(6日)胃部劇痛送院死亡。其妻子今日(7日)早上7時許在陳之社交網站facebook發貼，向陳之好友公布其已離世的死訊，指昨晚9時許，洋名Steven的陳突然在家中暈倒，送院搶救後不治。陳生前的好友得知後，紛紛感到難過及突然，並且留言安慰陳妻。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，陳已婚並育有一名女兒，為一名註冊社工，在新界區一社福機構服務，<span style=\"color: red;\">對跨境學童問題非常關注，常參與一些與內地交流的活動</span>。陳亦熱愛家庭、國家，以及無辣不歡，經常在社交網站貼上一家三口溫馨家庭合照，<span style=\"color: red;\">以及參與內地活動的照片</span>。又不時貼上不少以辣椒入饌的美食。據悉，陳近日有胃病，家人曾勸他就診，惟陳因忙於工作，未能抽空接受檢查。"},{"pid":"d2d98ecf72a22d6a84c9fd88434f8b1b13d6e705","tid":1095585,"uid":60831,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3a2672c8ebf26617d8051ea43fb4ecb94833c5","tid":1095585,"uid":42188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d2d98ecf72a22d6a84c9fd88434f8b1b13d6e705","tid":1095585,"uid":60831,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"連登仔集體炒車，琴日先係隔離post話人地唔係垃圾，為社會貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗯，為支那學童服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceff011d369c24b5ddeae85f3356443b67822b4","tid":1095585,